title: #138 - PewDiePie Hits 100M & James Charles Gets Hacked
description: On this episode of The H3 Podcast we talk about our boy Felix hitting 100M subs, our other boy James Charles' ass implants, we settle the Popeyes vs Chick-Fil-A debate once and for all, we talk about the World of Warcraft and how we may never see our loved ones again as a result, and a whole lot more!
